util
Class ModelInfo

java.lang.Object
  util.ModelInfo

public class ModelInfo
extends java.lang.Object

This class parses info-files for additional 3d-model information and makes them accessible.
Caution: This class doesn't take care of errors made by the user, that is, erroneous 3d-models can lead to undefined behaviour.

Not the best implementation since I discovered the java.util.Scanner for better parsing but hey.. it works!
